Package: taskforge
Architecture: all
Depends: python3:any, ${misc:Depends}, python3-appdirs, python3-autobahn, python3-docopt, python3-toml
Suggests: python3-github, python3-pymongo
Description:task management CLI that integrates with existing tools
 .
 taskforge is similar to taskwarrior but with a focus on
 integrating with existing task management systems. In
 this way it requires external dependencies such as
 python3-github or python3-pymongo if you wish to store
 you task data in a remote data store and will suggest
 these installations.
 .
 Note that all of these suggested dependencies are not
 required only those that correspond to the remote data
 stores you would like to use.